<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> However, most interchangeable-lens digital cameras do not use 24x36 mm <a href="/wiki/Image_sensor" title="Image sensor">image sensors</a> and therefore produce narrower angles of view than set out in the table. See <a href="/wiki/Crop_factor" title="Crop factor">crop factor</a> and the subtopic <b>digital camera issues</b> in the article on <a href="/wiki/Wide-angle_lens" title="Wide-angle lens">wide-angle lenses</a> for further discussion.</li>
